Source: langfuse-worker-@MAJOR@
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://langfuse.com/

Package: langfuse-worker-@MAJOR@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libssl3t64, zlib1g, libzstd1
Conflicts: langfuse-worker-2, langfuse-worker-3
Description: Langfuse worker (background job processor) version @MAJOR@
 Background job processor for the Langfuse LLM engineering platform. Handles
 evaluation jobs, ingestion, batch export, data retention, and integration
 queues over a Redis-backed BullMQ. The Node.js runtime is supplied by the
 consuming image; this package ships the built worker payload and its
 production node_modules under /usr/lib/nodejs/langfuse-worker.
